tika.dc.description: Ten tried and true finger food recipes from home cooking expert Jo Seagar.Jo Seagar's name is synonymous with stress-free recipes. She adores entertaining and cooking for friends, and always has a houseful of people staying. With this mouth-watering selection Jo shares ten of her easy finger food ideas, suitable for any occasion.
